{
  "stem": "311.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was set up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there must of be some kind of repair shop in that factory. the factory was like almost 200,000 square feet, 1 floor, 18-foot ceilings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One of the best heating systems I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was like 10-inch pipes all around, you know, steam pipes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was nice and comfortable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could wash something and just hang it up on the pipe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food was good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing is, it was in a place, in-- in Czechoslovakia, where you could eat a horse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The air was so terrific over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is like-- [SIGHS] how can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Plazow didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- I had-- not that I had enough.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had enough with the money, with everything we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But over there, for some kind of reason, I never had cereal in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bruennlitz, yeah, this was the name of the town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I understand the work, what we had right away, he must have get it from Skoda.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was only a mile or two away from us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Skoda is the biggest factory in the world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Skoda, this was under one roof, they did everything, from-- from a car to a sewing machine, to-- to a bullet, to anything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the sleeping quarters, it was-- it was like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say there's 200,000 square feet was the place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had a downstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was like [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] elongated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On one side was his quarters, Schindler, his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was one side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were upstairs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were steps, you know, quite wide, something like 12-foot wide, you know, steps to go upstairs, concrete, everything solid.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And upstairs, there were made up, like in Plazow, we had three layers.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
